Algorithm for Complex Transfer Tax Computation for complex 

create a function that will be called by the system to compute the transfer tax


Deed of Absolute Sale on a Portion of Land

Requirements:
1. Owner of the property are all alive and signed the notarized document
    User add the following information:
        Notarial Documents such as Doc No., Page No., Book No., Notarized By, Notarized Date
        Transaction Info such as Type, Consideration, Days From Notarial
2. search for the property in the database
3. if the property is found in the database, get the following information:
    Owner Name
    tax dec number
    lot number 
    area 
    market value
    assessed value
4. Add the data to the transaction list temporary storage (cookies) for computation
5. User select in the transaction list the property that will be included in the computation
6. A prompt will be shown asking for the following information:
    how many area or sq.m. is being transferred
    compute the new market value of the portion = market value / area * area being transferred
    assign new lot number for the portion
    assign new tax dec number for the portion
7. Add the portion to the transaction list for computation
8. Add the parties involved such as transferee and transferor
9. User will input the consideration amount base on the notarized document
10. Compute the transfer tax for the portion
11. Save the computaion to the transafer tax list 
12. User can print the computation sheet

