create a complex computation of transfer tax for the following:

Deed of Extrajudicial Settlement 

1. Search for the property in the database
2. If found get the following information:
    Owner Name
    tax dec number
    lot number 
    area 
    market value
3. List all the owner of the property and determine if the owner is deceased or alive
4. System will count the number of owner by the ';' separator
    User can select the owner who are deceased and the system will compute the share of the deceased owner
5. To compute the share of the of the deceased owner, the system will divide the market value by the number of owners
6. System will add the share of the deceased owner to the transferee
7. User will click the add to computation button to add the property to the transaction list for computation
8. System will loop back to step 1 if the user wants to add more properties to the transaction list for computation
9. System will update the owner of the properties transferred to heirs and remove the deceased owner from the owner list
10. System will compute the transfer tax for the share of the deceased owner
11. System will generate report for the computation of the transfer tax for the share of the deceased owner

