2. User will select the property/ies that will be included in the computation
3. System will compute the transfer tax base on the market value of the portion or consideration whichever is higher
4. use the rate of 75% of 1 % = 0.0075
5. System will generate report for the computation of the transfer tax for the extradjudicial settlement with simultaneous of sale


